st.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Carbon-Tax-per-Country_Shareable_04102024-400x240.jpg" class="mvp-reg-img lazy wp-post-image" alt="显示碳税收入排名前 15 位的国家的图表。" srcset="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Carbon-Tax-per-Country_Shareable_04102024-400x240.jpg 400w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Carbon-Tax-per-Country_Shareable_04102024-1000x600.jpg 1000w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Carbon-Tax-per-Country_Shareable_04102024-590x354.jpg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="80" height="80" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Carbon-Tax-per-Country_Shareable_04102024-80x80.jpg" class="mvp-mob-img lazy wp-post-image" alt="显示碳税收入排名前 15 位的国家的图表。" srcset="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Carbon-Tax-per-Country_Shareable_04102024-80x80.jpg 80w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Carbon-Tax-per-Country_Shareable_04102024-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Carbon-Tax-per-Country_Shareable_04102024-100x100.jpg 100w" sizes="(max-width: 80px) 100vw, 80px" /></div><!--mvp-blog-story-img--><div class="mvp-blog-story-in"><div class="mvp-blog-story-text left relative"><div class="mvp-cat-date-wrap left relative"><span class="mvp-cd-cat left relative">绿色</span><span class="mvp-cd-date left relative">2 个月前</span></div><!--mvp-cat-date-wrap-->碳税收入排名前15位的国家</h2><p>该图突出显示法国和加拿大在产生碳税收入方面处于全球领先地位。 </p></div><!--mvp-blog-story-text--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-in--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-out--></li><li class="mvp-blog-story-wrap left relative infinite-post"><div class="mvp-blog-story-out relative"><div class="mvp-blog-story-img left relative"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="400" height="240" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/shareable-4-400x240.jpg" class="mvp-reg-img lazy wp-post-image" alt="显